text: Ashkadarovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Sabyrovsky Selsoviet, Zilairsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 169 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 45 km from Zilair, 10 km from Sabyrovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zilairsky District
title: Ashkadarovo
